data.description: Beautiful North Vacaville single story home, with great curb appeal! This 3bed/2bath home has updated roof, paid off solar, and dual pane windows with plantation shutters. Kitchen has lots of cupboards, recessed lighting and granite counters including extra room for seating. The large and spacious dining area has lovely designer glass doors that open to a beautiful backyard and a large patio. Oversized family room is great for entertaining or just relaxing. Master bedroom has lots of closet space & sliding glass doors which open to the backyard, that has its own sitting area. The side yard has a shed and planter boxes. Landscaped front and backyards have been beautifully maintained with automated sprinklers and a drip system for the vegetation. This home has newer interior and exterior paint along with a new garage door. Home is near schools, parks, shopping and close freeway access. This home won't last long!
